'''克里斯多福·約翰·平徹'''（{{lang-en|Christopher John Pincher}}<ref>http://www.ukwhoswho.com/view/article/oupww/whoswho/U251091/</ref>，{{bd|1969年|9月24日}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/35491.stm |title=Christopher Pincher MP |publisher=BBC |work=BBC Democracy Live |date= |accessdate=25 July 2010 |archive-date=2013-09-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130912213618/http://news.bbc.co.uk/democracylive/hi/representatives/profiles/35491.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]政治人物，他的黨籍是[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]。他在1987年加入該黨<ref name="Parliament biography">{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.uk/biographies/christopher-pincher/35491|title=Christopher Pincher|author=|date=|work=|publisher=Parliament|accessdate=15 July 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110701162625/http://www.parliament.uk/biographies/christopher-pincher/35491|archivedate=2011年7月1日}}</ref>。自2010年開始，他擔任[[塔姆沃思_(英國國會選區)|塔姆沃思]]選區選出的英國下議院議員<ref name="Labour MP of 14 years loses">{{cite news |title=Labour MP of 14 years loses seat to Tories in Tamworth |first= |last= |url=http://www.birminghampost.net/news/politics-news/2010/05/07/labour-mp-of-14-years-loses-seat-to-tories-in-tamworth-65233-26395057/ |newspaper=Birmingham Post |date=7 May 2009 |accessdate=11 June 2011 |archive-date=2010-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101224114017/http://www.birminghampost.net/news/politics-news/2010/05/07/labour-mp-of-14-years-loses-seat-to-tories-in-tamworth-65233-26395057/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年7月起任歐美國務大臣。

